- to list all branches in a repository

git branch

- to remove a branch from a repository

git branch -d <name of branch>

- to quickly create a new branch

git checkout -b <name of new branch>

- to stage a file

git add <name of file>

- to commit the file with a comment included

git commit -a -m 'comment goes here'

- to push changes to the origin branch (on github)

git push origin <name of branch>

- to pull a branch

git pull <name of branch>

- to know the status of a branch

git status

- to delete a remote branch (on github)

$ git push origin --delete <name of branch>
